nodes.text: Kyrf was a liquor made by distilling and fermenting the kyrf fruit native to the planet Korbin. When fermented, kyrf liquor was very flavorful and potent to Humans, whom were very prone to its intoxicating effects. Korbin's indigenous scrub lizards were immune to intoxication by kyrf. Korbinites, who were mostly human, were largely kyrf-addicts.
